                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="mengapa-menyempurnakan-gerakan-sholat-jumat-bukan-merupakan-hal-yang-dapat-merusak-pelaksanaan-sholat-jumat">
                            28. Mengapa menyempurnakan gerakan sholat jumat bukan merupakan hal yang dapat merusak pelaksanaan sholat jumat?</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Karena menyempurnakan gerakan shalat jumat termasuk sunat shalat jumat</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="kapan-sholat-jumat-dilakukan-dan-apa-hukum-sholat-jumat-bagi-kaum-laki-laki%e2%80%8b">
                            29. Kapan sholat jumat dilakukan dan apa hukum sholat jumat bagi kaum laki laki​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>sholat Jumat hukumnya wajib bagi laki-laki</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>maaf kalau salah</p><p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p><strong>S</strong><strong>H</strong><strong>O</strong><strong>L</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>T</strong><strong> </strong><strong>J</strong><strong>U</strong><strong>M</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>T</strong><strong> </strong><strong>D</strong><strong>I</strong><strong>L</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>K</strong><strong>U</strong><strong>K</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>N</strong><strong> </strong><strong>S</strong><strong>E</strong><strong>T</strong><strong>I</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>P</strong><strong> </strong><strong>H</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>R</strong><strong>I</strong><strong> </strong><strong>J</strong><strong>U</strong><strong>M</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>'</strong><strong>T</strong><strong>,</strong><strong> </strong><strong>D</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>N</strong><strong> </strong><strong>H</strong><strong>U</strong><strong>K</strong><strong>U</strong><strong>M</strong><strong> </strong><strong>B</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>G</strong><strong>I</strong><strong> </strong><strong>L</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>K</strong><strong>I</strong><strong>-</strong><strong>L</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>K</strong><strong>I</strong><strong> </strong><strong>Y</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>I</strong><strong>T</strong><strong>U</strong><strong> </strong><strong>W</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>J</strong><strong>I</strong><strong>B</strong><strong> </strong><strong>D</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>N</strong><strong> </strong><strong>B</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>G</strong><strong>I</strong><strong> </strong><strong>P</strong><strong>E</strong><strong>R</strong><strong>E</strong><strong>M</strong><strong>P</strong><strong>U</strong><strong>A</strong><strong>N</strong><strong> </strong><strong>I</strong><s